# Nx/EXLA

## Setup

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:nx, "~> 0.1.0-dev", github: "elixir-nx/nx", sparse: "nx", override: true},
  {:exla, "~> 0.1.0-dev", github: "elixir-nx/nx", sparse: "exla"}
])
```

```elixir
Nx.Defn.global_default_options(compiler: EXLA)
```

## Stuff

```elixir
t = Nx.iota({3, 3})
```

## Numerical definitions

```elixir
defmodule Calc do
  import Nx.Defn

  defn cube(t) do
    Nx.power(t, 3)
  end
end
```

```elixir
Calc.cube(t)
```
